{"body": "It appears that this pull request also parses invalid dates that were previously not parsed.\r\n\r\nFor example, \"3333333INVALID\" is now parsed as a valid date, whereas in previous versions of rails it was not.\r\n\r\nI think this is a pretty big regression, and it means that I have to validate all of my user-entered dates manually now.\r\n\r\nWhat do you think?  If I reverted this commit, I think it would ease the Rails 4 transition considerably.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/21990973", "created_at": "2013-08-02T07:41:56Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/8722#issuecomment-21990973", "updated_at": "2013-08-02T07:41:56Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 8722, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zilkey/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zilkey/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zilkey/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/zilkey", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zilkey/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/zilkey", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zilkey/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/c84807bb5457755ec17ba32ff713a9b2?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F2dbf21633f03afcf882eaf10e4b5caca.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zilkey/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zilkey/received_events", "gravatar_id": "c84807bb5457755ec17ba32ff713a9b2", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zilkey/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "zilkey", "type": "User", "id": 2451, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/zilkey/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523d74d7bd354364b9006ead"}, "id": 21990973, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/8722"}
